We need to prove that if the sets {x | p x} and {x | p' x} are in the neighborhood filter of x, and similarly for {x | q x} and {x | q' x}, then the set {x | p x ∧ q x ∨ p' x ∧ q' x} is also in the neighborhood filter of x.

